<PB N="209" REF="027249_0207_0FD3ED4ADE6261A0">tho&s;e occa&s;ions; men who &s;pend their whole time in drink|ing gaming, and whoring, admitted to the table of the Lord, to &s;erve a turn in pol<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">es, contrary to every rule di|vine and h<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">man; and yet tho&s;e men commence the pillars and governors of the church, without coming near its a&s;&s;em|blies on other occa&s;ions. The&s;e things make amazingly for our imere&s;t.</P>
