<P>You do me great honour, my &s;on, and have my per|mi&s;&s;ion to proceed; but as I have urgent bu&s;ine&s;s in hand, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">d am already acquainted with your &s;tory, I &s;hall leave you for the pre&s;ent, and meet you here to-morrow. Darkne&s;s and confu&s;ion attend you all.</P>
